    <rdfs:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Source: EU AI Act — EU AI Act, Annex IV, Point 2(g) (chunk EUAI_AnnexIV_Point2_g)</rdfs:comment>
