    <rdfs:label rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">The period during which documentation must be kept, as specified in the EU AI Act.</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Source: EU AI Act — EU AI Act, Article 18(1)(a) (chunk EUAI_Art18_Para1_e)</rdfs:comment>
