    <rdfs:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Source: DUAA 2025 — DUAA 2025, Section 80, Article 22D(3)(b) (chunk DUAA_S80_Art22D_3_b)</rdfs:comment>
