    <rdfs:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Source: DUAA 2025 — DUAA 2025, Schedule 6 — Automated decision-making: amendments to GDPR Art 13(2)(f) and Art 14(2)(g) (chunk DUAA_Sch6)</rdfs:comment>
  </rdf:Description>
