    <rdfs:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Source: EU AI Act — EU AI Act, Article 16(1) — Obligations of providers of high-risk AI systems(a) (chunk EUAI_Art16_Para1_a)</rdfs:comment>
  </rdf:Description>
